# Initialize a new Configuration

Start a new Logik Configuration. Payload must include:

```json
"partnerData": {
    "product": {
        "configuredProductId": "<configProductId>"
     }
},
```

where `configProductId` is the Product Id of a Logik enabled configurable Product.

# Update a Configuration

Pass an array of field objects to update specific variables in the configuration

```json
    "fields": [
        {
            "variableName": "<var1>",
            "value": <var1val>
        },
        {
            "variableName": "<var2>",
            "value": <var2val>
        }
    ]
```
